Product:UHJvZHVjdDoxMjM3MTY=.description: Hill’s Science Diet Adult Sensitive Stomach & Skin Small & Mini Breed Chicken Recipe may be crafted for small and toy breed adult dogs, but it sure packs big benefits! It features natural ingredients, like real animal protein first and it’s packed with antioxidant benefits, too. It’s also formulated to help provide optimal digestive health and help nourish the skin. You’ll love knowing that it’s backed by decades of cutting-edge research, and your dog will love the way every bite tastes!

keyBenefits: Contains prebiotic fiber to help feed your small buddy’s microbiome for optimal digestive health.
Omega-6 fatty acids, vitamin E and other nutrients help nourish skin and promote a lustrous coat.
Helps provide miniature and toy breed dogs with an optimal balance of nutrients.
Made in the USA with highly digestible ingredients from around the world you can trust. This kibble is great for canine companions with sensitive stomachs and sensitive skin.
Crafted with natural ingredients with added vitamins, minerals and amino acids.

itemSubHeader.richText: If you've got a sensitive pup, try Hill's Science Diet Adult Sensitive Stomach & Skin Dog Food with precise nutrition to help support her healthy lifestyle. Made with wholesome ingredients such as savory chicken meal and barley, this nourishing recipe will help meet your dog's nutritional needs and nourish her skin and coat. Manufactured in the United States, every ingredient meets strict requirements for purity and nutrient content which exceed industry standards. Formulated for adult dogs with sensitive stomachs, Hill's Science Diet Adult Sensitive Stomach & Skin provides your pooch with the nutrition she needs for a lifetime of health and happiness.

header.text: Precisely Balanced Nutrition for Sensitive Stomachs and Skin

itemSubHeader.richText: The right combination of protein, fats, and carbs gives your small dog the energy he needs to thrive.
Made with the special Hill’s antioxidant blend for lifelong immune support.
Whether your dog prefers crunchy kibble or savory stews, these recipes have textures and flavors that deliver.
An expert team of veterinarians, nutritionists, and food scientists create the right nutrition to support pets.
Hill’s is a leader in cutting-edge food science and research, so they can bring you the best for your pet.
The ingredients Hill’s uses are selected for their nutrients, quality, and taste, then precisely blended for optimal health benefits.

Every time you feed your pet Hill’s, you help feed a shelter pet—which helps makes them healthy, happy, and more adoptable. Hill’s is proud to have helped over 13 million shelter pets find a new home through their shelter feeding initiatives.

The healthiest pet food won't do much if pets refuse to eat it. From a rich aroma to various textures, every Hill's recipe is taste-tested by the pets at the Pet Nutrition Center to make sure mealtime is irresistible. Using natural ingredients and cutting-edge science, Hill's understands what it takes to feed your pet's best life.                                                                                 
*Dry foods only
